text: Józef Wiśniewski (1 November 1940 – 9 January 1996), was a Polish former ice hockey player. He played for TKH Toruń during his career. He also played for the Polish national team at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1940 births Category:1996 deaths Category:Ice hockey players at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Olympic ice hockey players of Poland Category:People from Toruń County Category:Sportspeople from Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship Category:Polish ice hockey goaltenders Category:TKH Toruń players
